  "title": "Janitor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Info:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Basic $1,600 - $2,000</li>\n  <li>5 day per week, 9.30am - 2.30pm </li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Perform thorough cleaning and maintenance tasks in designated areas</li>\n  <li>Ensure adequate supply levels by restocking items such as toilet paper and hand soap</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness within the pantry/janitor/emptying trash</li>\n  <li>Vacuum or sweeping the floors.</li>\n  <li>Manage waste disposal by emptying rubbish bins and clearing trash into designated disposal areas</li>\n  <li>Cleaning of shower room</li>\n  <li>Diligently sanitize tabletops, shelves, and partitions to uphold hygiene standards</li>\n  <li>Promptly report any instances of damaged items or suspected issues to appropriate personnel</li>\n  <li>Fulfill any additional responsibilities as assigned by the superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
